[SN]TITLE[SN]
Falmouth chickens get winter woolies to keep warm

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman from Falmouth in Cornwall is knitting jumpers for her hens to keep them warm and raise money for charity.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
12 November 2015 Last updated at 18:10 GMT
Chicken owner Nicola Congden and her mother Ann hit on the idea after feeling sorry for their intake of battery hens which had lost many of their feathers.
